        "timestamp": "2020-02-10 15:35:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Why do we have separate nodes for each type of profile? \n> I suggest to have a generic profile node with type/role/function to differentiate each of the profile.\n\nBecause each profile has different attributes,as i reported on 2020-1-8 AAI weekly meeting.\n\nIf define a generic profile, it will be difficult to differentiate each profile.",
